2024: A Bold Year of Explore | Notion
hubeiqiao.notion.site

Also, here is a quick update on a few items:
1. I=E2=80=99ve contacted several companies regarding the Perplexity =
campaign. Elicit responded with an offer of 500 Plus licenses for $2,500 =
annually, though it doesn=E2=80=99t meet our goals. I=E2=80=99ll follow =
up with them post-holidays and plan to reach out to Anthropic directly =
to explore potential educational collaborations.

2. For the Perplexity event, I aim to present practical, real-world use =
cases like =E2=80=9CMaster Your Assignments with Perplexity Space: A =
Step-by-Step Guide"=C2=A0 =
<https://hubeiqiao.notion.site/Master-Your-Assignments-with-Perplexity-Spa=
ce-A-Step-by-Step-Guide-1590df12ec7780cfaf68e7359eef2127?pvs=3D4>on =
campus in January to prepare for the February workshop. If we need the =
